1. Decide which pizzeria you are ordering from
2. Go through the menu 
3. Decide what type of pizza you would like to order
4. Place the order by calling the pizzeria
5. Make an online payment
6. Wait on the delivery man to deliver the pizza
7. Open the door to collect your pizza from the delivery man
8. Tip the delivery man and say thank you
9. Open up pizza and devour
10. Put leftovers away in the fridge
11. Break down pizza box 
12. Put box with recycling 